e":"2019-09-08T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bede1d2a27e843320d4613584ccf3d09ec34f2f5","tid":1553010,"uid":275402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"感謝勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d372e0a08c166c037d8e7b6a059a7c31f27436","tid":1553010,"uid":39427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:29:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">識唱嘅大家一齊唱</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=73563f42\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《願榮光歸香港》  </strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Glory be to thee, Hong Kong</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land</span><br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand</span><br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die</span><br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">As we yearn, our freedom nighs</span><br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With eyes blinded, long it comes the night</span><br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight</span><br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song</span><br />\n建自由 光輝 香港  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air</span><br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!</span><br />\n捍自由   <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We shall strike</span><br />\n來齊集這裡  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">This perilous night</span><br />\n來全力抗對  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Determined to fight</span><br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With hope, with song, with dignity!</span><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!</span><br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!</span><br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides</span><br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q4kAzyW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ4kAzyW.jpg&h=84f48da3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">英文譯版原post<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》英文歌詞 &quot;Glory be to Thee, Hong Kong&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547782\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547782</a></span>"},{"pid":"e4d5962c7359a6276a2fbe3464170104ccd04ac8","tid":1553010,"uid":247614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:30:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8caae27976767ecee1b2a30e1aa1c18f5ae7181e","tid":1553010,"uid":139277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:35:11.000Z","msg":"+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想錫曬你地春袋 好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123ef66c4aa0b48be68dad909bca595ae44ec617","tid":1553010,"uid":163485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score